data.description: Move in ready North Royalton Split level  with 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths!  The front door opens to a spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and new laminate flooring.  Kitchen complete with granite counters, ceramic floors and newer appliances.  The family Room has a fireplace and patio doors overlooking the stamped concrete patio.  Laundry Room on the main level complete with washer and dryer.  Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms and one full bath. The large master bedroom has access to the bathroom and a large walk-in closet.  The basement is partially finished and is perfect for another entertaining room or playroom.  Updates-A/C 2020, Dishwasher 2019, Stamped Patio in 2014. Furnace 2010. Shed 2010. Garage door 2012. Siding, Gutters, Trim and Soffit 2006 & H2O 2007.  1yr Home warranty included from 2-10 Home Warranty $549.00     This home is Move-in Ready!
